{"tid":1993194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《買雞排行動長文》施捨solo行動者","createTime":"2020-04-28T15:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T16:48:42.000Z","uid":69314,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c173232a8b01ec80309ede957f78d7a47abbd426","tid":1993194,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:10:50.000Z","msg":"原post: 【求求大家幫下我】我想買沙律<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1920779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1920779</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n事實上不想用施施捨兩個字<br />\n<br />\n可是，這個月能找的人和組織都找，也沒有辦法<br />\n<br />\n東躲西藏的日子，不見天日，壓力大得想自殺，也很害怕被自己和去坐<br />\n<br />\n在這最後，謝謝幫忙和關心我的人，而數字即使去到四位數字我也謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n記得上個post有師兄提出用加幣貨幣，純粹不想成為第二個車手的局面<br />\n<br />\n在這，只能一試，看看能否夠錢買雞排，這次失敗我會自己去找狗拼個生死，所得的錢也會交給還未被凍結的組織，累積去拯救下一個香港人<br />\n<br />\n年少時期，早半年的我認為錢不是萬能，光復香港的理念能夠戰勝全部，香港人的團結光輝一面一次一次感動我，可是慢慢地，發現金錢是罪惡，令一個一個手足用盡方法掛着名號享受生活，香港人互相猜度，但真正有良心的卻因為金錢而一個一個消失<br />\n<br />\n尚差距金額 : 6位數字頭<br />\n<br />\nBitcoin 銀包 : <br />\nbc1qd88ygntyyqjpkezl72wt6lx6cztjduu5k5zx9d<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PaNQpEF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPaNQpEF.jpg&h=4c0c122e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不論能否買到雞排與否，我會找方法把所得金額公佈，只取自己夠買雞排的錢，不夠或多額的也會公佈。<br />\n<br />\n我請天主作證一切所言的真偽，和日後所為<br />\n<br />\n有猜忌和存疑者，請不要作出捐錢，接受一切的批評和問題，不是說服你們捐錢買雞排，只為自己作證，和借眾人審視自己<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我生香港<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"86e554e1b0981a9c6a7770295000135599fd4f00","tid":1993194,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231d10d20924f28c4ec79c0dbf209f1d689e158f","tid":1993194,"uid":151544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86e554e1b0981a9c6a7770295000135599fd4f00","tid":1993194,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:37:42.000Z","msg":"保密度高又唔使比錢眾籌"},{"pid":"e29daa37f7c24efaa3c866b34a56a19c301bc64f","tid":1993194,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86e554e1b0981a9c6a7770295000135599fd4f00","tid":1993194,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12b684ea230290001e05af09d37e3d5167f7bcd","tid":1993194,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e29daa37f7c24efaa3c866b34a56a19c301bc64f","tid":1993194,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86e554e1b0981a9c6a7770295000135599fd4f00","tid":1993194,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940f3c697c8c614f8d7650860dbbf144e5be98ab","tid":1993194,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137c92763e97948b72b46179a45c28ec38a8fdae","tid":1993194,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c12b684ea230290001e05af09d37e3d5167f7bcd","tid":1993194,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e29daa37f7c24efaa3c866b34a56a19c301bc64f","tid":1993194,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86e554e1b0981a9c6a7770295000135599fd4f00","tid":1993194,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":